Nigeria movie sensation,  Ali  Nuhu, has signed a new football deal as an influencer of the Spanish league brand, La Liga reports judicialsketch.com. The actor confirmed  the development  on the fringe of the La Liga fans meeting held in Kano last Sunday  but declined  the to disclose the worth   of the  deal. “I guess because of COVID-19 many did not know about the deal,” stated Nuhu. “I cannot disclose how much but everything is not all about money,”Nuhu said. He said the new deal contracts him to influence the La Liga brand, noting that he is expected to travel to Spain to further strengthen the relationship. Nuhu said the deal has provided him with the platform to further nurture and empower northern youths through football.